Text:
I'm totally bummed I misspelled  the band's name in the keyword tag. Hopefully everyone notices I spelled it right everywhere else and on my other torrent, so I am not a complete idiot; my fingers just got ahead of my brain. I take it edit has been "temporarily" disabled for a long time.

Thanks to the other seeders. 

A damn good show. Lots of Weir material that didn't get played as often as some other tunes. I was psyched that Alabama Getaway was on here too but it was kind of mediocre.
